3402	\begin{lemma}[An epimorphism of sheaves is locally surjective]
3403	  \label{lem:sheaf_locally_surjective_iff_epi}
3404	  \lean{CategoryTheory.Sheaf.isLocallySurjective_iff_epi'}
3405	  \mathlibok
3406	  \uses{lem:presheaf_is_locally_surjective}
3407	  \textit{Provided by Mathlib.}
3408	  A morphism of sheaves (of abelian groups, valued in a suitable category) is an epimorphism in the
3409	  category of sheaves if and only if it is locally surjective. In particular an epimorphism of
3410	  abelian sheaves on the space \(X\) is locally surjective, supplying the covering with local lifts
3411	  used in Step 2 of Lemma~\ref{lem:affine_surj_of_vanishing}.
3412	\end{lemma}
